Meghan Markle Wears Sneakers for the First Time in a Royal Appearance|http://www.elle.com|http://www.elle.com/culture/a24019367/meghan-markle-sneakers-first-time-royal-appearance/||2018-10-21|Ariana Yaptangco||Meghan Markle is known for her impeccable royal style and the mom-to-be made another major fashion statement during her Australian tour with Prince Harry. Typically spotted in elegant heels at official royal appearances, the Duchess opted for a cool pair of sustainable sneakers for her most recent outing.

