Getty Images

According to the Daily Mail, this is the first time Meghan has worn sneakers to a royal appearance, choosing leather V-10s from sustainable fashion brand Veja. The comfortable shoes make sense, as the Sussexes took in the 2018 Sydney Invictus Games by boat.

Despite her royal heel-wearing, Meghan has a fond history with flats. She was a big fan of a comfy slipper-like pair that made appearances on her now-deleted Instagram account (RIP) which we just so happened to track down.

